WEBVTT

00:04:29.344 --> 00:04:32.322
was in her role as "babaylan,"

00:04:33.236 --> 00:04:37.657
a collective term for shamans
of various ethnic groups.

00:04:37.681 --> 00:04:40.070
They were the community healers,

00:04:40.094 --> 00:04:43.180
specialists in herbal and divine lore.

00:04:44.160 --> 00:04:45.448
They delivered babies

00:04:45.472 --> 00:04:47.733
and communicated with the spirit world.

00:04:48.677 --> 00:04:50.497
They performed exorcisms

00:04:51.489 --> 00:04:54.743
and occasionally, and in defense
of their community,

00:04:55.767 --> 00:04:57.498
they kicked some ass.

00:04:57.522 --> 00:04:59.149
(Laughter)

